sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / DSP Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>:9090 metrics, :6060 healthz
    participant CronCtrl as Cron Controller<br/>(in workflow-controller)
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod<br/>(created by controller)
    participant ArgoExec as argoexec (sidecar)<br/>Emissary pattern
    participant S3 as S3 / Minio<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    K8sAPI-->>WFC: Informer notification<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    WFC->>K8sAPI: Create Pod (workflow step)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    K8sAPI-->>Pod: Pod scheduled

    Note over ArgoExec,S3: Init Container Phase
    ArgoExec->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>ArgoExec: Artifact data

    Note over Pod: Main container executes

    Note over ArgoExec,S3: Wait Container Phase
    ArgoExec->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    ArgoExec->>K8sAPI: Patch WorkflowTaskResult<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer

    WFC->>DB: Archive workflow (optional)<br/>Auth: Secret credentials<br/>PostgreSQL/TLS

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    CronCtrl->>K8sAPI: List CronWorkflows<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    K8sAPI-->>CronCtrl: CronWorkflow list
    CronCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow from schedule<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: Artifact Garbage Collection

    WFC->>K8sAPI: Create WorkflowArtifactGCTask<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    WFC->>K8sAPI: Create GC Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer
    Note over ArgoExec,S3: GC Pod executes
    ArgoExec->>S3: Delete expired artifacts<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
